Capital Markets

Company Overview of Macquarie Capital Investment Management LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Macquarie Capital Investment Management LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to investment companies. It also caters to pooled investment vehicles and pension and profit sharing plans. The firm manages client focused portfolios. It also manages equity and balanced mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets across the globe and fixed income markets. It typically invests in companies engaged in infrastructure activities or emerging market securities. The firm employs a fundamental, technical, and charting analysis to make its investments. It uses internal and external research to make its investments. The firm wa...
Macquarie Capital Investment Management LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to investment companies. It also caters to pooled investment vehicles and pension and profit sharing plans. The firm manages client focused portfolios. It also manages equity and balanced mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets across the globe and fixed income markets. It typically invests in companies engaged in infrastructure activities or emerging market securities. The firm employs a fundamental, technical, and charting analysis to make its investments. It uses internal and external research to make its investments. The firm was founded on January 14, 2004 and is based in the New York City. Macquarie Capital Investment Management LLC operates as a subsidiary of Macquarie Group Limited.
Detailed Description


125 West 55th StreetNew York, NY 10019United StatesFounded in 2004



